```

вЬЕ Debounce, retry logic

***

## 4пЄПвГ£ Error Handling in Saga

Use standard `try / catch`:

```js
function* fetchSaga() {
  try {
    const data = yield call(api.fetch);
    yield put({ type: "SUCCESS", data });
  } catch (error) {
    yield put({ type: "FAILURE", error });
  }
}
```

вЬЕ Very common interview topic

